# ====================================================================
# Academy Curriculum Suite — Environment variables
# اختبر منتجك أو فكرتك بالبداية مع المهندس عبدالعزيز
# ====================================================================
#
# The app runs fully offline without any of these variables set.
# All AI operations fall back to deterministic mock generators that
# produce realistic, structured output — suitable for demos, MVP, and
# full end-to-end usage.
#
# Set these variables ONLY when you want to enable real AI generation
# via your own server-side proxy.
#
# ⚠️  NEVER put raw AI provider keys here — they would be exposed to the
# browser. Always proxy requests through a backend that holds the key.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# Optional: URL of your server-side AI proxy (Claude / Gemini / OpenAI)
# The proxy must accept POST { model, system, prompt, temperature, max_tokens }
# and return { text } OR Anthropic-native { content: [{ text }] }.
# VITE_CLAUDE_PROXY_URL=https://your-proxy.example.com/claude

# Optional: model identifier forwarded to the proxy (free-form)
# VITE_CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-6
